STATE of North Carolina
v.
Shamonte Arnell GREEN. No. 345P06. Supreme Court of North Carolina. October 5, 2006. Barbara S. Blackman, Matthew D. Wunsche, Assistant Appellate Defenders, for Green. Beirne M. Harding, Assistant District Attorney, Robert C. Montgomery, Special Deputy Attorney General, Thomas J. Keith, for State.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 28th day of June 2006 for Writ of Supersedeas of the Order of the Forsyth County Superior Court, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Forsyth County Superior Court:

"Dismissed as Moot by order of the Court in conference, this the 5th day of October 2006."
